N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 1260.5 - List of certificates of acceptability

State Regulations

The State Fire Prevention and Building Code Council shall
establish a list of certificates of acceptability issued pursuant to this Part, to be maintained at the office of the chairperson, for public review during
regular business hours. Notes
